    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Lists or invoices of cargo on a ship, usually containing marks or indication of contents or commodity, consignee, and other pertinent information for use at terminals or customhouses.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
